epiphallic complex ventral, 
<emphasis id="13B5EAECFFEDFFA8FC69F851FC3D01A7" bold="true" box="[957,971,1947,1969]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">b</emphasis>
epiphallic complex lateral, 
<emphasis id="13B5EAECFFEDFFA8FB2DF851FAF201A7" bold="true" box="[1273,1284,1947,1969]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">c</emphasis>
gonocoxite &amp; gonostyli ventral, 
